 is, you can SWITCH to GOtv JINJA or JOLLI for more choice entertainment With GOtv JOLLI bouquet you will get to enjoy – international movies on TNT Africa channel, urban Naija movies and series on ROK 2, exciting series on CBS Reality and FOX, and stimulate your children’s minds with educational content on Da Vinci Learning If you are a GOtv Plus customer… switch to GOtv JOLLI for only N2,400 per month While GOtv JINJA gives you local Naija movies on Africa Magic Epic, entertaining reality shows with FOX Life and Realtime while keeping children engaged with PBS Kids. If you are a GOtv Value customer… switch to GOtv JINJA for only N1,600 per month Naija! It’s time to leave old for NEW. Effective 1st June, GOtv Value & GOtv Plus bouquets will be phased out and customers migrated to the brand new GOtv JINJA & GOtv JOLLI. And yes, if you SWITCH to the new packages ‘GOtv JINJA or GOtv JOLLI’ this MONTH (before 31st May) … You automatically get UPGRADED to the next higher package at no extra cost. That’s a special discount offer for GOtv Value or Plus customers… when you switch to JINJA or JOLLI respectively. So what are you waiting for? get better entertainment and much more content on the new packages or other package options on GOtv Now is the time to JOLLI & JINJA yourself. Download MyDStv App from the app store or visit www.gotvafrica.com for more information or other self-service options. GOtv Dey Your Side. To show appreciation to subscribers for their support and patronage during these challenging times, GOtv is offering amazing DISCOUNT on their subscription. GOtv is rewarding its customers with mouth-watering discounts of up to 75%. Active and disconnected GOtv customers are eligible to enjoy discounts on upgraded viewing for captivating local dramas, thrilling series, movies,… May 5, 2020 In "Sponsored" To lessen the impact of the ongoing socio-economic crisis, MultiChoice has announced that it will be rewarding DStv and GOtv subscribers, who are fully paid up